Uses of Class
remodel.expr.Expression

Packages that use Expression 
Package Description
remodel.expr
Metamodel components to represent ReMoDeL expressions.
remodel.io
Components for reading, writing and compiling ReMoDeL models, metamodels and transformations.

  • Uses of Expression in remodel.expr

    Subclasses of Expression in remodel.expr 
    Modifier and Type Class Description
    class  ApplicationExpression
    ApplicationExpression is a kind of MultipleExpression denoting the application of a functional rule.
    class  AssignmentExpression
    AssignmentExpression is a kind of BinaryExpression denoting an assignment.
    class  BinaryExpression
    BinaryExpression is a kind of OperatorExpression with two operands.
    class  BracketedExpression
    BracketedExpression is a kind of WrappedExpression denoting another Expression wrapped in parentheses.
    class  CompoundExpression
    CompoundExpression is a kind of MultipleExpression denoting a sequence of statements.
    class  ConditionalExpression
    ConditionalExpression is a kind of Expression denoting an if-then-else binary branching construction.
    class  CreationExpression
    CreationExpression is a kind of MultipleExpression denoting the creation of an object.
    class  IdentifierExpression
    IdentifierExpression is a kind of Expression denoting a named identifier.
    class  InvocationExpression
    InvocationExpression is a kind of MultipleExpression denoting the invocation of a message on a receiver.
    class  LambdaExpression
    LambdaExpression is a kind of WrappedExpression denoting a lambda function passed as an argument to an Operation.
    class  LiteralExpression
    LiteralExpression is a kind of Expression denoting a literal value.
    class  MultipleExpression
    MultipleExpression is the abstract ancestor of Expressions that contain multiple sub-Expressions.
    class  OperatorExpression
    OperatorExpression is the abstract ancestor of Expressions that have an operator.
    class  UnaryExpression
    UnaryExpression is a kind of OperatorExpression with a single operand.
    class  WrappedExpression
    WrappedExpression is the abstract ancestor of Expressions containing a single encapsulated Expression.
